INT. CAVE IN THE SIGHTLESS EYE 

THE PLAYER faces MEPHISTO warily. The sound of his DEMONIC WHISPERS CRESCENDOES.
He SNIFFS the Player. They stand their ground nervously as he begins to CIRCLE them. Same demonic whispers as heard in CBH.

The Player hesitantly gets on one knee as Mephisto sits. They peer at the wolf with trepidation, but Mephisto holds their gaze placidly. 

His eyes begin to BURN, and the fire spreads around his head. As it does, the same effect appears on the Player, starting in their eyes, then traveling.

Subtle VFX spark into life around their head. It PERSISTS even as the two separate. 

Mephisto’s form begins to distort, his body starting to fade.

Mephisto disappears completely. The Player STANDS TALL, filled with newfound direction and DETERMINATION. 

TRANSITION TO GAMEPLAY.
